{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/How-long-Banner.png?t=1734303017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Snowsquall Grip </strong>is a short horror/thriller game with PSX/Retro aesthetics where the player gets lost amid a sudden snowstorm.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/for-gif-1.gif?t=1734303017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>THE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Primary: Walking simulator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intuitive Physics-Based Item Interaction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Straightforward Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Low on Jumpscares: Emphasis on the Atmospheric Exploration</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/for-gif-2.gif?t=1734303017\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/for-gif-3.gif?t=1734303017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive Emergency Scenario</strong>: Trapped in an unforgiving snowstorm in the style of PSX horror games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No Inventory, Only Instinct</strong>: With no inventory to rely on, every essential item for survival must be manually grabbed and utilized with precision.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Battle the Elements</strong>: Fight against the biting cold to maintain your sanity, as you navigate through the relentless snowsquall.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Uncover Creepy Secrets</strong>: Piece together the eerie mysteries lurking within the storm's icy grip.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Escape or Perish</strong>: Will you summon the courage to confront the unknown and find your way out, or succumb to the icy depths of this frozen nightmare, forever lost in its chilling embrace?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/for-gif-4.gif?t=1734303017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>THE STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In their relentless pursuit of the ultimate energy source, scientists from Modern-City, under the leadership of The Supreme One, established a hidden facility to study a mysterious radiation seeping from beneath a thick ice layer, far from civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maintaining this operation demands a constant supply of special energy batteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your task is to deliver these batteries. What starts as a routine delivery mission quickly unravels into a journey that sheds light on the dark secrets of the elusive energy known in the future as &quot;Re.Surs&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/jewel_case-snowsquall--opt.gif?t=1734303017\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE GAME IS PART OF THE &quot;RE.SURS UNIVERSE&quot; GAME SERIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>[RE.SURS] [PLASTOMORPHOSIS]</strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"CRASH","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3000420/88652b1e82cb61150009e0cca686275d1917e310.jpg"},{"name":"LONER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3000420/77c7c853a11372da0df6f8a8092c460a7099c9ae.jpg"},{"name":"DELIVERY","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam